-- ============================================================================
-- earnings-test-v0-final-static2.sql   (CITY 2)
--
-- STATIC version. Works in prod today, no Haskell deploy required.
--
-- Every uiTranslation is a plain string literal (UiTrPlain). No key lookup,
-- no template substitution, no vars. Zero risk of decode failure on the
-- consumer side. The numeric amount is still carried in price.amount /
-- price.currency, which the UI renders alongside the text.
--
-- Same 22-branch logic as v0-final, same merge skeleton, same conditions.
-- Only the uiTranslation shape changes.
--
-- City:     ce6a69ac-d7c0-4393-939e-03cdfdebae5d
-- Merchant: a7f3c8e2-4b5d-4c9a-8f6e-2d1a3b4c5d6e
--
-- WHAT FIRES, WHEN — same as v0-final:
--   * 3 always-on (toll/discount/commission)  — fire when value > 0
--   * 16 diff flat-field pairs (incr/decr)    — fire when ride vs booking differ
--   * 6 ProgressiveDetails pairs (incr/decr)  — additionally require Progressive tag
-- ============================================================================


-- 0. DROP PRIOR STATE  ------------------------------------------------------

